ActPublic Sector Pension Investment Board Act
PrecisAppointment of CHRISTOPHER FOWLER of Edmonton, Alberta, to be a director of the Public Sector Pension Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years, in the place of Martin Glynn, whose term has expired.
